					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In ASM6 you can &quot;shift&quot; the character codes from their normal ASCII codes like this:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">.db &quot;ABCDEF&quot;-65</div><br />This string will appear in the ROM as $00, $01, $02, $03, $04, $05.</div>

